91, \"to\": 207}, {\"ngram\": \"five Olympic medals\", \"from\": 234, \"to\": 253}, {\"ngram\": \"total\", \"from\": 257, \"to\": 262}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the 400m freestyle champion is not impressed with what the athletes are dealing with in Paris when it comes to their living conditions.\", \"from\": 265, \"to\": 409, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 362, \"end\": 367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999937558641, \"rank\": 6.244190532351311e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 400m freestyle champion\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 301}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 329, \"to\": 341}, {\"ngram\": \"their living conditions\", \"from\": 385, \"to\": 408}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She won the 400m freestyle on Saturday, but was disappointed that she could not break her own world record in the process.\", \"from\": 411, \"to\": 533, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 400m freestyle\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 437}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 449}, {\"ngram\": \"her own world record\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 517}, {\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 532}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It probably wasn't the time I thought I was capable of, but living in the Olympic Village makes it hard to perform,' Titmus said on Sunday.\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 675, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 610, \"end\": 625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.159787889771958e-15, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}, {\"begin\": 653, \"end\": 659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5